CAARS_32.Description: Identifies inconsistencies in responding by summing the differences between responses to related questions: absolute value(question 3 - question 21) + absolute value(question 17- question 18) + absolute value(question 6 – question 10) + absolute value(question 4 - question 11) + absolute value(question 13 – question 20) + absolute value(question 7 – question 8) + absolute value(question 15 – question 16) + absolute value(question 9 – question 26) | Calculation = abs_f([CAARS_03]-[CAARS_21])+ abs_f([CAARS_17]-[CAARS_18])+ abs_f([CAARS_06]-[CAARS_10])+ abs_f([CAARS_04]-[CAARS_11])+abs_f([CAARS_13]-[CAARS_20])+abs_f([CAARS_07]-[CAARS_08])+abs_f([CAARS_15]-[CAARS_16])+ abs_f([CAARS_09]-[CAARS_26])
